Tonight (some of) the nation will be glued to the second "debate" between 7, yes 7, party leaders. I'm not sure how we'll learn anything from 7 voices in a mere 120 minutes (less adverts) but at least it gave Moo and their friend [Stacie Snoddon](http://www.perfektiondesign.com/) the chance to produce these outstanding sigils.
